dulge 1.0 - March 2026
=======================

This is the first release of dulge, a fork of the dulge package manager.

Major changes from upstream dulge:
- Rebranded from "dulge" to "dulge".
- Helper tools renamed: makepkg → dulge-build, repo-add → dulge-repo-add, etc.
- Build recipe filename changed from PKGBUILD to DULGEBUILD.
- Metadata files updated to credit the original Arch Linux team and the fork maintainer.
- All translations removed; users are directed to the upstream dulge project.

For a complete list of changes, see the git history.
